values.description: Manage signatures, agreements, and documents in PandaDoc
values.overview:
Connect to your PandaDoc account to manage your documents, contacts, and templates in PandaDoc. Increase your team’s productivity by keeping your PandaDoc account up to date - without manual data entry.
              
Our PandaDoc integration enables you to:
           
• Programmatically send documents from your PandaDoc account 
• Manage agreements in your PandaDoc account
• Sync documents in your PandaDoc account

Connect your Google account and sync events with your Google Calendar. Increase your productivity by ensuring your schedule is always up to date - without manual data entry.
 
Our Google Calendar integration enables you to:
 
• Automatically add new events to your Google Calendar
• Sync events from your Google Calendar

values.overview:
Connect to your Close account to manage your opportunities, contacts, and leads in Close. Increase your team’s productivity by keeping your Close account up to date - without manual data entry.
   
Our Close integration enables you to:
   
• Create or update records in your Close account
• Sync records from your Close account
• Receive webhooks when records are created or updated in your Close account
